<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795349>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6−11. Willowsia trifascia sp. nov. 6, scale; 7, proximal part of antenna; 8, eyes; 9, distal part of manubrium and proximal part of dentes; 10, hind claw; 11, dorsal chaetotaxy of Abd. V. Scale bars: 6 = 10μm, 7−11 = 20μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795349/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795351>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12−19. Willowsia trifascia sp. nov. 12, apex of Ant. IV; 13, distal part of Ant. III; 14, distal part of Ant. II; 15, dorsal chaetotaxy of head; 16, labrum; 17, lateral process of labial palp; 18, labium; 19, maxillary outer lobe. Scale bars: 12−19 = 20μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795351/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795355>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20−23. Willowsia trifascia sp. nov. 20, chaetotaxy of Th. II−III; 21, coxal macrochaetal formula of fore leg; 22, coxal macrochaetal formula of middle leg; 23, coxal macrochaetal formula of hind leg. Scale bars: 20−23 = 20μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795355/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795357>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24−26. Willowsia trifascia sp. nov. 24, trochanteral organ; 25, hind foot complex; 26, chaetotaxy of Abd. I−III. Scale bars: 24−26 = 20μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795357/files/figure.png" ;
