    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795363>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28−34. Willowsia trifascia sp. nov. 28, chaetotaxy of Abd. IV; 29, anterior face of ventral tube; 30, posterior face of ventral tube; 31, lateral flap of ventral tube; 32, manubrial plaque; 33, ventro-apical part of manubrium; 34, mucro. Scale bars: 28−34 = 20μm." ;
